<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email - COMSATS Internship Portal</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #6366f1 50%, #818cf8 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="verify-pattern" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23verify-pattern)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo-container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .header-title {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .header-subtitle {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            color: #e0e7ff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .verification-icon {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .verification-icon-circle {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #10b981);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 48px;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            animation: bounce 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 53%, 80%, 100% { transform: translate3d(0,0,0); }
            40%, 43% { transform: translate3d(0,-15px,0); }
            70% { transform: translate3d(0,-7px,0); }
            90% { transform: translate3d(0,-2px,0); }
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .greeting-highlight {
            color: #059669;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #10b981);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .verification-notice {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .verification-notice h3 {
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .verification-notice p {
            color: #a16207;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .cta-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .cta-button::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5);
        }
        
        .security-info {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .security-info h4 {
            color: #334155;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .security-info ul {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .security-info li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-warning {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            background-color: #fff8dc;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .token-info {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #93c5fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1e40af;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .header-title {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
            
            .verification-icon-circle {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                padding: 16px 32px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <div class="logo">
                    <div style="color: #4f46e5; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(79,70,229,0.3); letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1;">
                        COMSATS
                    </div>
                    <div style="color: #6366f1; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 600;">
                        UNIVERSITY
                    </div>
                    <div style="width: 40px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f46e5, #818cf8); margin-top: 8px; border-radius: 1px;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="header-title">EMAIL VERIFICATION</h1>
            <p class="header-subtitle">COMSATS Internship Portal</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Verification Icon -->
            <div class="verification-icon">
                <div class="verification-icon-circle">EMAIL</div>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="greeting">Verify Your Email, <span class="greeting-highlight">{{name}}</span>!</h2>
            
            <p class="message">
                You're just one step away from accessing the COMSATS Internship Portal! Please verify your email address to activate your account and start your journey.
            </p>
            
            <div class="verification-notice">
                <h3>Quick Verification Required</h3>
                <p>Your account has been created successfully, but you need to verify your email address before you can log in and access your dashboard.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-container">
                <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="cta-button">Verify My Email</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-info">
                <h4>Security Information</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>This verification link will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong></li>
                    <li>The link can only be used once</li>
                    <li>If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email</li>
                    <li>Never share your verification link with others</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="token-info">
                Having trouble with the button? Copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
                <strong>{{verificationUrl}}</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>COMSATS Internship Portal Team</strong>
            </p>
            
            <div class="footer-warning">
                <strong>Do not reply to this email.</strong> This is an automated verification message.
                <br>If you need help, please contact us through the portal after verification.
            </div>
            
            <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                Â© {{currentYear}} COMSATS University Internship Portal. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>